01:35:24,947 --> 01:35:26,614
Sama sekali bukan.

1308
01:35:27,449 --> 01:35:29,617
Aku cuma ingin kau paham.

1309
01:35:31,203 --> 01:35:33,955
Sebab aku sayang padamu dan
kaulah sahabat terbaikku.

1310
01:35:36,750 --> 01:35:38,543
Kau paham?

1311
01:35:38,711 --> 01:35:40,670
Ya, aku paham.

1312
01:35:44,425 --> 01:35:45,800
